title: Tasmania records ninth coronavirus death
description: The Premier has extended retail restrictions in place on Tasmania's north-west coast, as the state records its ninth coronavirus death.
content:
Updated 
April 24, 2020 10:01:39
Tasmania has recorded another coronavirus death overnight after a 79-year-old woman died in the Launceston General Hospital (LGH).
It takes the state's death toll to nine.
